Day39_Recap
 Topic Recap
        OOP Encaplsulation
        OOP Inheritance



  Shape:
        variables:
                name

        Encapsulate the filed
        Add a constructor to set the field
        Methods:
               area(){}
               perimeter(){}


    Square extends Shape:
         variables:
             side:

         Encapsulate the field
         Add a constructor to set the field

         area(): side * side
         perimeter(): side * 4
         toString() : side, area, perimeter

    Rectangle extends Shape:
         variables:
            length
            width

         Encapsulate the field
         Add a constructor to set the field

         area(): length * width
         perimeter(): 2 * (width)


    Circle extends Shape:
          variables
             radius
             pi
          Encapsulate the field
         Add a constructor to set the field

    Triangle extends Shape:

         Encapsulate the field
        Add a constructor to set the field